title: BEAUTIFUL, HUGE, CLASSIC UPPER DUPLEX IN S. MPLS/WEDGE AVAIL SEPT 1
posting_body: ['BEAUTIFUL, SPACIOUS UPPER DUPLEX, 1500 sq.', 'ft.  ENTIRE 2ND FLOOR OF LARGE VICTORIAN HOME.', ' The 3 LARGE BEDROOMS each have LARGE CLOSETS and two of the bedrooms have their own SUNROOMS.', ' This classic apartment features HARDWOOD MAPLE FLOORS throughout, a LARGE LIVING ROOM, BAY WINDOW with STAINED GLASS, a LARGE FORMAL DINING ROOM and a GENEROUS KITCHEN with DISHWASHER and newer STAINLESS STEEL GAS STOVE.', ' OFF-STREET PARKING is included and LAUNDRY is on the premises.', ' The building is wired for HIGH SPEED FIBER OPTIC INTERNET through US INTERNET.', 'This lovely home was pictured on the cover of a story in the SOUTHWEST JOURNAL extolling the Wedge as a great livable neighborhood.', 'This is the BEST LOCATION on a QUIET, FRIENDLY STREET in the WEDGE in South Minneapolis.', " A short walk to Lake of the Isles and a couple of blocks to shops (Wedge Co-op, Kowalski's, ALDI) and many restaurants (French Meadow, Common Roots, Nightingale and many more).", ' Also theatres, parks, museums and the bike greenway.', 'One block to Downtown bus or Express bus to U of M.', 'THIS IS A QUIET BUILDING which is well maintained by its attentive owner-occupant.', ' NO LOUD MUSIC or PARTIES ALLOWED.', 'Maximum occupancy for this apartment is 3 persons.', 'A ONE YEAR LEASE is required.', 'Available September 1st.', 'Water and Garbage is included.', ' Tenants pay Heat and Electric.', 'References are Required.', ' This is a NON-SMOKING BUILDING.', 'Sorry, NO PETS.', 'FOR A FASTER, BETTER RESPONSE PLEASE CALL ME  at', 'show contact info', '(this is a LAND LINE -NO TEXTS!)', 'and I will be happy to set up an appointment for you to see the apartment.']
